General.Name: Impellam Group Plc
General.Description: Impellam Group plc provides staffing solutions, human capital management, and outsourced people-related services in the United Kingdom, rest of Europe, North America, and the Asia Pacific. It operates through Global Managed Services and STEM. The Global Managed Services segment engages in the provision of multi-disciplinary workforce solutions under the Guidant Global, Comensura, and Flexy brand names. The STEM provides workforce and specialist recruitment solutions for IT, digital and data specialists, scientists, clinicians, and engineers under the Bartech, Carbon60, SRG, and Lorien brand names. The company was incorporated in 2008 and is based in Luton, the United Kingdom.
